Answer in whatever length necessary for completeness.

Consult the AT Lead if you're unable to locate answers.


    Does SPARC run 64-bit code?
    What's endianness? Is SPARC a big or little-endian architecture?
    Why is it so important to respect the user's CFLAGS on SPARC?
